<title>BELGIUM: Belgian IPSO-ILG offer eight times oversubscribed.</title>
<headline>Belgian IPSO-ILG offer eight times oversubscribed.</headline>
<dateline>BRUSSELS 1997-06-20</dateline>
<text>
<p>An initial public offer (IPO) of shares in Belgian industrial laundry equipment maker IPSO-ILG on the Brussels Stock Exchange has been eight times oversubscribed, the company said on Friday.</p>
<p>The offer closed on June 18, two days early.</p>
<p>IPSO-ILG said it had curtailed orders for its shares, favouring small investors. Individuals who had applied for more than 1,000 shares would receive only 40.</p>
<p>The shares are due to list in Brussels on June 27.</p>
